lead_paragraph: When Jose Fernandez threw a slider for his 14th strikeout to escape a seventh-inning jam, he spun on the mound, pumped his arms, screamed, pounded his glove, screamed some more and yanked at his jersey as though trying to tear it off.

headline.print_headline: Fernandez Outpitches Harvey, Marlins Beat Mets 1-0
